      <title>土耳其竞相加入金砖国家，力争建立超越西方的联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/turkey-submits-bid-to-join-brics-as-erdogan-pushes-for-new-alliances-beyond-west</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，土耳其已正式请求加入金砖国家新兴市场国家集团，以增强其全球影响力并与传统西方盟友建立新的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/turkey-submits-bid-to-join-brics-as-erdogan-pushes-for-new-alliances-beyond-west</guid>
