      <title>预算短缺 哈萨克斯坦考虑提高银行税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/kazakhstan-eyes-heftier-taxes-on-banks-amid-budget-shortfall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈萨克斯坦总统再次呼吁对该国银行征收更“公平”的税负，他表示，在政府努力缩小预算赤字之际，这些银行被认为是“世界上资源丰富的国家中最赚钱的银行之一”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/kazakhstan-eyes-heftier-taxes-on-banks-amid-budget-shortfall</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 09:45:08 GMT</pubDate>
